  <h3>Want to know more about eXtension?</h3>
  <p>Visit <a href="http://about.extension.org">About eXtension</a>.  There you'll find links to various eXtension resources where you can learn more about the benefits of eXtension, discover how to get involved with your colleagues already participating,  or get started with the eXtension sites and services.</p>
  <h3>Need a direct contact?</h3>
  <p>See our <a href="http://about.extension.org/wiki/Contacts_for_eXtension_Services_and_Support">Contacts for eXtension Services and Support</a></p>
  
</div>
<div id="contact_col_two">
    <h4>Create a Get Satisfaction account</h4>
    <ul>
        <% if @user %>
        <li>Copy your OpenID: <strong>people.extension.org/<%= @user.login %></strong></li>
        <% end %>
        <li>Visit the <a href="http://getsatisfaction.com/session/new">Get Satisfaction login page</a> and paste your OpenID in the OpenID field</li>
        <li>Confirm your OpenID on the eXtension People site</li>
        <li>Finish creating your account at Get Satisfaction without having to make up another password to remember.</li>
    </ul>
</div>
